4400:Nanami didn't seem to feel guilty at all. She was laughing. I could feel myself getting furious. What a bratty little sister![%p]
4500:[name]梨深[line]Sorry, Taku. I didn't mean to lie to you like this.[%p]
4600:[name]七海[line]You don't need to apologize, Rimi. It's my brother's fault for being so clueless![%p]
4700:I dropped to my knees right there. I felt frustrated at being tricked. I felt angry that she was making fun of me for being worried.[%p]
4800:I didn't like it. I didn't like what Nanami had done at all.[%p]
4900:But more than that... I'd been worried about nothing. Nanami was just fine. She wasn't hurt.[%p]
5000:Knowing that made me feel so relieved, like all the tension that had been building up inside me had just disappeared.[%p]
5100:[name]梨深[line]Taku, you okay?[%p]
5200:[name]七海[line]Come on, Brother. Don't be glum. Stand up.[%p]
