5400:[name]七海[line]Let's all go together![%p]
5500:Nanami really was a huge brat. She was always making fun of her big brother.[%p]
5600:I stood up, a little reluctantly, and with a small pouting look on my face.[%p]
5700:Nanami and Rimi smiled at each other. One took my left hand, and another my right.[%p]
5800:The two of them pulled me along as we started to walk. I could feel like my life was about to change for the better.[%p]
5900:A peaceful, bright future was awaiting me.[%p]
